Good afternoon Raffaella

Apologies for the delay in responding to your email and thank you for your =
patience.

Just letting you know that I=E2=80=99ve processed the settlement to your no=
minated account, as confirmed by you, covering the temporary accommodation =
and cleaning costs to date.

I will appear in your account as two separate payments one for the temporar=
y accommodation and the other for cleaning costs.

Please reply to this email for any further costs incurred for either the Co=
ntents or the Temporary Accommodation as both will be paid under this Conte=
nts claim as is the higher of the two benefits for Temporary Accom

Please reply to this email with details of any further costs incurred relat=
ing to either the Contents or Temporary Accommodation. Both will be paid un=
der this Contents claim, as it provides the higher of the two benefits for =
Temporary Accommodation.
Let me know if you have any questions or need assistance with submitting fu=
rther expenses.

Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or require further details.

Kind Regards


Sasha C
